long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A Twitter Bookmark alternative. Helpful with  following functions: 
1. Like any tweets anonymously, privately, we value your privacy, nobody know who and what you like. 
2. Use AI to summarize tags for your tweets automatically. 
3. With filter and search functions to find the tweets you like easily. You can filter by tags, authors. You can search by keyword as well.
4. Filter all tweets with videos.
